<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <title>CertGate - 고객문의</title>
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width,initial-scale=1">
  <%= csrf_meta_tags %>
  <%= csp_meta_tag %>
  
  <meta name="current-user" content='<%= current_user.to_json(only: [:id, :email, :name, :role]) if user_signed_in? %>'>
  
  <style>
    body {
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, sans-serif;
    }
    #app {
      min-height: 100vh;
    }
  </style>
</head>

<body>
  <div id="app"></div>
  
  <script type="module">
    // Vue dev server will inject the app here
    // In production, you'll need to build the Vue app and serve it from Rails
    window.location.href = 'http://localhost:5173/tickets/new';
  </script>
  
  <noscript>
    <div style="text-align: center; padding: 50px;">
      <h1>JavaScript가 필요합니다</h1>
      <p>이 페이지를 사용하려면 JavaScript를 활성화해 주세요.</p>
    </div>
  </noscript>
</body>
</html>
